definition: to accumulate/to hold in store/to contain/to gather together/to collect/depth/inner strength/profundity
to store up/to grow (e.g. a beard)/to entertain (ideas)

sentences.english: We have latent talents and dormant faculties, which are brought to light by exercise.
sentences.chinese: 我們蘊蓄着的天才和才能必須藉運用才發揮無餘。

sentences.english: Within it, at all times, it contains its whole potential.
sentences.chinese: 在它體內，在它生命的每時每刻，蘊蓄着全部潛能。
